&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll manage a portfolio of enterprise life sciences clients from implementation through ongoing growth — serving as the primary strategic partner for their Patient Services and Field Access programs. You&#39;ll sit at the intersection of delivery, strategy, and relationship, translating client needs into outcomes on both sides.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a role for someone who wants to do consequential work. You&#39;ll have real influence over how Courier Health shows up for its clients, how the Client Solutions practice evolves, and ultimately, how many patients get the support they need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You&#39;ll Build&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive client outcomes and expansion.&lt;/strong&gt; You own the long-term health of your client relationships. Success means your clients are hitting their goals, renewing, and expanding. You&#39;ll identify opportunities for clients to get more value from Courier Health and partner with our commercial team to pursue them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic advisory and thought partnership.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll advise client leadership on Patient Services and Field Access strategy based on cross-client patterns, program data, and deep familiarity with their business. You’re comfortable challenging the status quo and asking “why”.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client relationships that hold up under pressure.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll earn trust with day-to-day users and client executive leadership alike — not just by being responsive, but by knowing their business well enough to see around corners. You&#39;ll become the partner they call when things get complicated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A feedback loop that makes the product better.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll be close enough to clients to hear what&#39;s working and what isn&#39;t — and credible enough internally to make sure that feedback shapes the roadmap. You&#39;ll be a key input into how Courier Health evolves its platform and service offering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop the people around you.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll mentor junior team members; helping them think strategically about accounts, grow their client instincts, and accelerate their careers. Strong operators here become leaders.&lt;/p&gt;
