&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work directly with senior client executives and engineering teams on high-stakes launches where the details matter. You&#39;ll shape how we implement, not just execute someone else&#39;s playbook — the methodology, tooling, and best practices are still being built, and you&#39;ll help build them. If you want real ownership over outcomes that reach patients, this is it.&lt;/p&gt;
