&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clients who adopt, not just sign.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll lead discovery sessions to understand each client&#39;s program goals, patient journey workflows, and data sources, then document requirements and produce the solution design that guides the build. You&#39;ll run client-facing training and write the documentation that makes adoption stick. Going live is the start, not the finish line.&lt;/p&gt;
